{
  "video_id": "PxQcnxSbivQ",
  "title": "Shimon Steinberg: Natural pest control ... using bugs!",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15760.0,
      "end_time": 17759.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a bug lover, myself --"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17783.0,
      "end_time": 19536.0,
      "text": "not from childhood, by the way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19560.0,
      "end_time": 21130.0,
      "text": "but rather late."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22157.0,
      "end_time": 23536.0,
      "text": "When I bachelored,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23560.0,
      "end_time": 26253.0,
      "text": "majoring in zoology at Tel Aviv University,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26277.0,
      "end_time": 28414.0,
      "text": "I kind of fell in love with bugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28438.0,
      "end_time": 30176.0,
      "text": "And then, within zoology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30200.0,
      "end_time": 33339.0,
      "text": "I took the course or the discipline of entomology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33364.0,
      "end_time": 35614.0,
      "text": "the science of insects."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36400.0,
      "end_time": 39202.0,
      "text": "And then I thought to myself, how can I be practical"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39226.0,
      "end_time": 42202.0,
      "text": "or help in the science of entomology?"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42560.0,
      "end_time": 45793.0,
      "text": "And then I moved to the world of plant protection --"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45817.0,
      "end_time": 48319.0,
      "text": "plant protection from insects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48343.0,
      "end_time": 50157.0,
      "text": "from bad bugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50181.0,
      "end_time": 52535.0,
      "text": "And then within plant protection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52560.0,
      "end_time": 56821.0,
      "text": "I came into the discipline of biological pest control,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56845.0,
      "end_time": 58535.0,
      "text": "which we actually define"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 58559.0,
      "end_time": 61535.0,
      "text": "as the use of living organisms"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 61560.0,
      "end_time": 66600.0,
      "text": "to reduce populations of noxious plant pests."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66840.0,
      "end_time": 69186.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s a whole discipline in plant protection"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 69210.0,
      "end_time": 72666.0,
      "text": "aimed at the reduction of chemicals."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73456.0,
      "end_time": 75502.0,
      "text": "And biological pest control, by the way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 75526.0,
      "end_time": 78294.0,
      "text": "or these \"good bugs\" that we are talking about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78318.0,
      "end_time": 82149.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve existed in the world for thousands and thousands of years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 82174.0,
      "end_time": 83777.0,
      "text": "for a long, long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 83801.0,
      "end_time": 87383.0,
      "text": "But only in the last 120 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 87488.0,
      "end_time": 90878.0,
      "text": "people started, or people knew more and more"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 90902.0,
      "end_time": 95288.0,
      "text": "how to exploit, or how to use, this biological control phenomenon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 95312.0,
      "end_time": 98692.0,
      "text": "or in fact, natural control phenomenon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 98716.0,
      "end_time": 100954.0,
      "text": "for their own needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 101440.0,
      "end_time": 105480.0,
      "text": "Because biological control phenomenon -- you can see it in your backyard."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 105720.0,
      "end_time": 108280.0,
      "text": "Just take a magnifying glass. You see what I have here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 108520.0,
      "end_time": 112660.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a magnifier, times 10."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 112900.0,
      "end_time": 115880.0,
      "text": "You just open it, twist leaves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 115112.0,
      "end_time": 118536.0,
      "text": "and you see a whole new world of minute insects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 118560.0,
      "end_time": 123536.0,
      "text": "or little spiders of one millimeter, one-and-a-half, two millimeters long,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 123560.0,
      "end_time": 126560.0,
      "text": "and you can distinguish between the good ones and the bad ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 126584.0,
      "end_time": 131124.0,
      "text": "So this phenomenon of natural control exists literally everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 131148.0,
      "end_time": 133202.0,
      "text": "Here, in front of this building, I&#39;m sure."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 133226.0,
      "end_time": 134748.0,
      "text": "Just have a look at the plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 135165.0,
      "end_time": 138826.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s everywhere, and we need to know how to exploit it."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 139329.0,
      "end_time": 141306.0,
      "text": "Well, let&#39;s go hand by hand"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 141330.0,
      "end_time": 144536.0,
      "text": "and browse through just a few examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 144560.0,
      "end_time": 146750.0,
      "text": "What is a pest?"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 146990.0,
      "end_time": 149409.0,
      "text": "What damage does it actually inflict on the plant?"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 149433.0,
      "end_time": 151694.0,
      "text": "And what is the natural enemy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 151718.0,
      "end_time": 154701.0,
      "text": "the biological control agent, or the \"good bug\""
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 154725.0,
      "end_time": 155926.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re talking about?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 155950.0,
      "end_time": 160963.0,
      "text": "In general, I&#39;m going to talk about insects and spiders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 160987.0,
      "end_time": 163210.0,
      "text": "or mites, let us call them."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 163234.0,
      "end_time": 166300.0,
      "text": "Insects, those six-legged organisms"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 166270.0,
      "end_time": 170105.0,
      "text": "and spiders or mites, the eight-legged organisms."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 170129.0,
      "end_time": 171536.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s have a look at that."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 171560.0,
      "end_time": 174788.0,
      "text": "Here is a devastating pest, a spider mite,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 174812.0,
      "end_time": 177684.0,
      "text": "because it does a lot of webbing, like a spider."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 178600.0,
      "end_time": 179582.0,
      "text": "You see the mother in between,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 179606.0,
      "end_time": 182160.0,
      "text": "and two daughters, probably, on the left and right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 182400.0,
      "end_time": 184108.0,
      "text": "and a single egg on the right-hand side."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 184132.0,
      "end_time": 186620.0,
      "text": "And then you see what kind of damage it can inflict."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 186644.0,
      "end_time": 189186.0,
      "text": "On your right-hand side, you can see a cucumber leaf,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 189210.0,
      "end_time": 190651.0,
      "text": "in the middle, a cotton leaf,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 190675.0,
      "end_time": 193873.0,
      "text": "and on the left, a tomato leaf with these little stipplings."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 193897.0,
      "end_time": 196950.0,
      "text": "They can literally turn from green to white,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 196974.0,
      "end_time": 202536.0,
      "text": "because of the sucking, piercing mouth parts of those spiders."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 203180.0,
      "end_time": 206688.0,
      "text": "But here comes nature, that provides us with a good spider."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 206712.0,
      "end_time": 210940.0,
      "text": "This is a predatory mite -- just as small as a spider mite;"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 210118.0,
      "end_time": 212922.0,
      "text": "one, two millimeters long, not more than that --"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 212946.0,
      "end_time": 217359.0,
      "text": "running quickly, hunting, chasing the spider mites."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 217384.0,
      "end_time": 221251.0,
      "text": "And here, you can see this lady in action on your left-hand side --"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 221276.0,
      "end_time": 226902.0,
      "text": "just pierces, sucks the body fluids on the left-hand side of the pest mite."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 226926.0,
      "end_time": 229536.0,
      "text": "And after five minutes, this is what you see:"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 229560.0,
      "end_time": 231879.0,
      "text": "just a typical dead corpse --"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 231903.0,
      "end_time": 235536.0,
      "text": "the shriveled, sucked-out, dead corpse of the spider mite,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 235560.0,
      "end_time": 240424.0,
      "text": "and next to it, two satiated individuals, predatory mites,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 240448.0,
      "end_time": 243945.0,
      "text": "a mother on the left-hand side, a young nymph on the right-hand side."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 243969.0,
      "end_time": 246891.0,
      "text": "By the way, a meal for them for 24 hours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 246915.0,
      "end_time": 251165.0,
      "text": "is about five of the spider mites, of the bad mites,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 251189.0,
      "end_time": 256740.0,
      "text": "and-or 15 to 20 eggs of the pest mites."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 256980.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258536.00000000003,
      "text": "By the way, they are always hungry."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 258560.0,
      "end_time": 260798.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 260822.0,
      "end_time": 263130.0,
      "text": "And here is another example: aphids."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 263154.0,
      "end_time": 265800.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s springtime now in Israel."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 265320.0,
      "end_time": 267537.0,
      "text": "When temperatures rise sharply,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 267561.0,
      "end_time": 270834.0,
      "text": "you can see those bad ones, those aphids, all over the plants --"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 270858.0,
      "end_time": 273536.0,
      "text": "in your hibiscus, in your lantana,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 273560.0,
      "end_time": 277536.0,
      "text": "in the young, fresh foliage of the so-called spring flush."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 277560.0,
      "end_time": 281536.0,
      "text": "By the way, with aphids you have only females, like Amazons."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 281560.0,
      "end_time": 284985.0,
      "text": "Females giving rise to females, giving rise to other females."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 285900.0,
      "end_time": 286238.0,
      "text": "No males at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 286262.0,
      "end_time": 288698.0,
      "text": "Parthenogenesis, as it&#39;s so called."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 288722.0,
      "end_time": 290837.0,
      "text": "And they&#39;re very happy with that, apparently."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 290861.0,
      "end_time": 291885.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 291910.0,
      "end_time": 293536.0,
      "text": "Here we can see the damage."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 293560.0,
      "end_time": 300320.0,
      "text": "Those aphids secrete a sticky, sugary liquid called honeydew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 300344.0,
      "end_time": 304363.0,
      "text": "and this just clogs the upper parts of the plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 304387.0,
      "end_time": 308100.0,
      "text": "Here you see a typical cucumber leaf that turned from green to black"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 308124.0,
      "end_time": 312843.0,
      "text": "because of a black fungus, sooty mold, which is covering it."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 312867.0,
      "end_time": 318195.0,
      "text": "And here comes the salvation, through this parasitic wasp."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 318219.0,
      "end_time": 320320.0,
      "text": "Here we are not talking about a predator."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 320345.0,
      "end_time": 322809.0,
      "text": "Here we are talking a parasite --"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 322833.0,
      "end_time": 324706.0,
      "text": "not a two-legged parasite,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 324730.0,
      "end_time": 327739.0,
      "text": "but an eight-legged parasite, of course."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 327763.0,
      "end_time": 329537.0,
      "text": "This is a parasitic wasp,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 329561.0,
      "end_time": 335316.0,
      "text": "again, two millimeters long, slender, a very quick and sharp flier."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 335340.0,
      "end_time": 338123.0,
      "text": "And here you can see this parasite in action,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 338148.0,
      "end_time": 340815.0,
      "text": "like in an acrobatic maneuver."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 340839.0,
      "end_time": 342536.0,
      "text": "She stands vis-à-vis"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 342560.0,
      "end_time": 344887.0,
      "text": "in front of the victim at the right-hand side,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 344911.0,
      "end_time": 350850.0,
      "text": "bending its abdomen and inserting a single egg"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 350109.0,
      "end_time": 352216.0,
      "text": "into the body fluids of the aphid."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 352898.0,
      "end_time": 355550.0,
      "text": "By the way, the aphid tries to escape."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 355790.0,
      "end_time": 359338.0,
      "text": "She kicks and bites and secretes different liquids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 359362.0,
      "end_time": 361412.0,
      "text": "but nothing will happen, in fact --"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 361436.0,
      "end_time": 364846.0,
      "text": "only the egg of the parasitoid will be inserted"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 364870.0,
      "end_time": 367800.0,
      "text": "into the body fluids of the aphid."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 367320.0,
      "end_time": 369967.0,
      "text": "And after a few days, depending upon temperature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 369992.0,
      "end_time": 371409.0,
      "text": "the egg will hatch"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 371433.0,
      "end_time": 376404.0,
      "text": "and the larva of this parasite will eat the aphid from the inside."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 376428.0,
      "end_time": 377479.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 377503.0,
      "end_time": 379747.0,
      "text": "This is all natural. This is all natural."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 379771.0,
      "end_time": 381770.0,
      "text": "This is not fiction, nothing at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 381794.0,
      "end_time": 384745.0,
      "text": "Again -- in your backyard. In your backyard."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 384769.0,
      "end_time": 386274.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 386298.0,
      "end_time": 387763.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 387787.0,
      "end_time": 394244.0,
      "text": "But this is the end result: mummies."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 394354.0,
      "end_time": 399536.0,
      "text": "This is the visual result of a dead aphid encompassing inside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 399560.0,
      "end_time": 405455.0,
      "text": "a developing parasitoid that, after a few minutes, you see halfway out."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 405479.0,
      "end_time": 407685.0,
      "text": "The birth is almost complete."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 407709.0,
      "end_time": 410883.0,
      "text": "You can see, by the way, in different movies, etc.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 410907.0,
      "end_time": 412536.0,
      "text": "it takes just a few minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 412560.0,
      "end_time": 416620.0,
      "text": "And if this is a female, she&#39;ll immediately mate with a male"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 416860.0,
      "end_time": 418922.0,
      "text": "and off she goes, because time is very short."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 418946.0,
      "end_time": 421536.0,
      "text": "This female can live only three to four days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 421560.0,
      "end_time": 425422.0,
      "text": "and she needs to give rise to around 400 eggs."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 425446.0,
      "end_time": 428848.0,
      "text": "That means she has 400 bad aphids"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 428872.0,
      "end_time": 431853.0,
      "text": "to put her eggs into their body fluids."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 432464.0,
      "end_time": 434440.0,
      "text": "This is, of course, not the end of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 434464.0,
      "end_time": 436846.0,
      "text": "There is a whole wealth of other natural enemies"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 436870.0,
      "end_time": 438536.0,
      "text": "and this is just the last example."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 438560.0,
      "end_time": 441530.0,
      "text": "Again, we&#39;ll start first with the pest:"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 441770.0,
      "end_time": 442536.0,
      "text": "the thrips."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 442560.0,
      "end_time": 444863.0,
      "text": "By the way, all these weird names --"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 444887.0,
      "end_time": 448386.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t bother you with the Latin names of these creatures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 448410.0,
      "end_time": 449650.0,
      "text": "just the popular names."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 449674.0,
      "end_time": 453786.0,
      "text": "But this is a nice, slender, very bad pest."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 453810.0,
      "end_time": 456158.0,
      "text": "If you can see this: sweet peppers."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 456182.0,
      "end_time": 459181.0,
      "text": "This is not just an exotic, ornamental sweet pepper."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 459205.0,
      "end_time": 461752.0,
      "text": "This is a sweet pepper which is not consumable"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 461776.0,
      "end_time": 464536.0,
      "text": "because it is suffering from a viral disease"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 464560.0,
      "end_time": 467725.0,
      "text": "transmitted by those thrip adults."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 468170.0,
      "end_time": 471687.0,
      "text": "And here comes the natural enemy, minute pirate bug --"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 471711.0,
      "end_time": 474290.0,
      "text": "\"minute,\" because it is rather small."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 474314.0,
      "end_time": 477733.0,
      "text": "Here you can see the adult, black, and two young ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 477757.0,
      "end_time": 479302.0,
      "text": "And again, in action."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 479326.0,
      "end_time": 482137.0,
      "text": "This adult pierces the thrips,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 482874.0,
      "end_time": 485120.0,
      "text": "sucking it within just several minutes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 485144.0,
      "end_time": 488374.0,
      "text": "going to the other prey, continuing all over the place."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 488398.0,
      "end_time": 492693.0,
      "text": "And if we spread those minute pirate bugs, the good ones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 492717.0,
      "end_time": 495613.0,
      "text": "for example, in a sweet pepper plot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 495637.0,
      "end_time": 497206.0,
      "text": "they go to the flowers."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 497230.0,
      "end_time": 502314.0,
      "text": "And look -- this flower is flooded with predatory bugs, with the good ones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 502338.0,
      "end_time": 505536.0,
      "text": "after wiping out the bad ones, the thrips."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 505560.0,
      "end_time": 508144.0,
      "text": "So this is a very positive situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 508168.0,
      "end_time": 511468.0,
      "text": "No harm to the developing fruit. No harm to the fruit set."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 511492.0,
      "end_time": 514556.0,
      "text": "Everything is just fine under these circumstances."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 515304.0,
      "end_time": 516765.0,
      "text": "But again, the question is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 516789.0,
      "end_time": 520991.0,
      "text": "here you saw them on a one-to-one basis -- the pest, the natural enemy."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 521357.0,
      "end_time": 524328.0,
      "text": "What we do is actually this."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 524804.0,
      "end_time": 528233.0,
      "text": "In Northeast Israel, in Kibbutz Sde Eliyahu,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 528257.0,
      "end_time": 532626.0,
      "text": "there is a facility that mass-produces those natural enemies."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 532971.0,
      "end_time": 539449.0,
      "text": "In other words, what we do there is amplify the natural control,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 539473.0,
      "end_time": 541449.0,
      "text": "or the biological control phenomenon."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 541474.0,
      "end_time": 546351.0,
      "text": "And in 30,000 square meters of state-of-the-art greenhouses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 546375.0,
      "end_time": 549679.0,
      "text": "there, we are mass-producing those predatory mites,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 549703.0,
      "end_time": 551398.0,
      "text": "those minute pirate bugs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 551422.0,
      "end_time": 554318.0,
      "text": "those parasitic wasps, etc."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 554342.0,
      "end_time": 555669.0,
      "text": "Many different parts."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 555693.0,
      "end_time": 557949.0,
      "text": "By the way, they have a very nice landscape --"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 557973.0,
      "end_time": 560348.0,
      "text": "you see the Jordanian Mountains on the one hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 560373.0,
      "end_time": 562350.0,
      "text": "and the Jordan Valley on the other hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 562374.0,
      "end_time": 566427.0,
      "text": "and a good, mild winter and a nice, hot summer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 566451.0,
      "end_time": 570446.0,
      "text": "which is an excellent condition to mass-produce those creatures."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 570470.0,
      "end_time": 574710.0,
      "text": "And by the way, mass-production -- it is not genetic manipulation."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 574734.0,
      "end_time": 578781.0,
      "text": "There are no GMOs -- genetically modified organisms -- whatsoever."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 578805.0,
      "end_time": 580536.0,
      "text": "We take them from nature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 580560.0,
      "end_time": 584857.0,
      "text": "and the only thing that we do is give them the optimal conditions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 584881.0,
      "end_time": 587536.0,
      "text": "under the greenhouses or in the climate rooms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 587560.0,
      "end_time": 590977.0,
      "text": "in order to proliferate, multiply and reproduce."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 591627.0,
      "end_time": 593318.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s what we get."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 593342.0,
      "end_time": 595199.0,
      "text": "You see under a microscope."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 595223.0,
      "end_time": 598367.0,
      "text": "You see in the upper left corner? You see a single predatory mite."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 598391.0,
      "end_time": 601786.0,
      "text": "And this is the whole bunch of predatory mites."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 601810.0,
      "end_time": 604130.0,
      "text": "You see this ampul. You see this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 604154.0,
      "end_time": 607330.0,
      "text": "I have one gram of those predatory mites."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 607651.0,
      "end_time": 611199.0,
      "text": "One gram is 80,000 individuals."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 611763.0,
      "end_time": 617349.0,
      "text": "80,000 individuals are good enough to control one acre,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 617373.0,
      "end_time": 619211.0,
      "text": "4,000 square meters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 619235.0,
      "end_time": 621880.0,
      "text": "of a strawberry plot"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 621112.0,
      "end_time": 624400.0,
      "text": "against spider mites for the whole season"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 624650.0,
      "end_time": 625478.0,
      "text": "of almost one year."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 626242.0,
      "end_time": 629790.0,
      "text": "And we can produce from this, believe you me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 629814.0,
      "end_time": 634216.0,
      "text": "several dozens of kilograms on an annual basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 634240.0,
      "end_time": 638448.0,
      "text": "So this is what I call amplification of the phenomenon."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 638472.0,
      "end_time": 642271.0,
      "text": "And no, we do not disrupt the balance."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 642295.0,
      "end_time": 643536.0,
      "text": "On the contrary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 643560.0,
      "end_time": 646443.0,
      "text": "because we bring it to every cultural plot"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 646467.0,
      "end_time": 649220.0,
      "text": "where the balance was already disrupted"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 649244.0,
      "end_time": 650536.0,
      "text": "by the chemicals."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 650560.0,
      "end_time": 652436.0,
      "text": "Here we come with those natural enemies"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 652461.0,
      "end_time": 655368.0,
      "text": "in order to reverse a little bit of the wheel"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 655392.0,
      "end_time": 659374.0,
      "text": "and to bring more natural balance to the agricultural plot"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 659398.0,
      "end_time": 661239.0,
      "text": "by reducing those chemicals."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 661263.0,
      "end_time": 662818.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the whole idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 662842.0,
      "end_time": 664280.0,
      "text": "And what is the impact?"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 664304.0,
      "end_time": 667536.0,
      "text": "In this table, you can actually see what is an impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 667560.0,
      "end_time": 671287.0,
      "text": "of a successful biological control by good bugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 671908.0,
      "end_time": 678277.0,
      "text": "For example, in Israel, where we employ more than 1,000 hectares --"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 678301.0,
      "end_time": 680976.0,
      "text": "10,000 dunams in Israeli terms --"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 681000.0,
      "end_time": 683625.0,
      "text": "of biological pests controlling sweet pepper"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 683649.0,
      "end_time": 685173.0,
      "text": "under protection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 685197.0,
      "end_time": 688852.0,
      "text": "75 percent of the pesticides were actually reduced."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 688876.0,
      "end_time": 691361.0,
      "text": "And Israeli strawberries, even more --"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 691385.0,
      "end_time": 693159.0,
      "text": "80 percent of the pesticides,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 693183.0,
      "end_time": 697751.0,
      "text": "especially those aimed against pest mites in strawberries."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 698106.0,
      "end_time": 699982.0,
      "text": "So the impact is very strong."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 701244.0,
      "end_time": 703392.0,
      "text": "And there goes the question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 703416.0,
      "end_time": 706393.0,
      "text": "especially if you ask growers, agriculturists:"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 706417.0,
      "end_time": 708110.0,
      "text": "Why biological control?"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 708134.0,
      "end_time": 709912.0,
      "text": "Why good bugs?"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 709936.0,
      "end_time": 712702.0,
      "text": "By the way, the number of answers you get"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 712726.0,
      "end_time": 714857.0,
      "text": "equals the number of people you ask."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 716314.0,
      "end_time": 720872.0,
      "text": "But if we go, for example, to this place, Southeast Israel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 720896.0,
      "end_time": 724372.0,
      "text": "the Arava area above the Great Rift Valley,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 724396.0,
      "end_time": 729440.0,
      "text": "where the pearl of Israeli agriculture is located,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 729465.0,
      "end_time": 733580.0,
      "text": "especially under greenhouse conditions, or under screenhouse conditions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 733820.0,
      "end_time": 735871.0,
      "text": "if you drive all the way to Eilat, you see this"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 735895.0,
      "end_time": 737808.0,
      "text": "just in the middle of the desert."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 737832.0,
      "end_time": 739341.0,
      "text": "And if you zoom in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 739365.0,
      "end_time": 741680.0,
      "text": "you can definitely watch this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 741456.0,
      "end_time": 743643.0,
      "text": "grandparents with their grandchildren,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 743667.0,
      "end_time": 746536.0,
      "text": "distributing the natural enemies, the good bugs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 746560.0,
      "end_time": 748933.0,
      "text": "instead of wearing special clothes"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 748957.0,
      "end_time": 751157.0,
      "text": "and gas masks and applying chemicals."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 751745.0,
      "end_time": 754331.0,
      "text": "So safety, with respect to the application,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 754355.0,
      "end_time": 757774.0,
      "text": "is the number one answer that we get from growers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 757798.0,
      "end_time": 759771.0,
      "text": "for \"Why biological control?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 760949.0,
      "end_time": 764919.0,
      "text": "Number two, many growers are, in fact, petrified"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 764943.0,
      "end_time": 768126.0,
      "text": "by the idea of resistance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 768150.0,
      "end_time": 772703.0,
      "text": "that the pests will become resistant to the chemicals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 772727.0,
      "end_time": 776536.0,
      "text": "just like in our case, that bacteria becomes resistant to antibiotics."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 776560.0,
      "end_time": 779328.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the same, and it can happen very quickly."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 780168.0,
      "end_time": 784536.0,
      "text": "Fortunately, in either biological control or even natural control,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 784560.0,
      "end_time": 787621.0,
      "text": "resistance is extremely rare."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 788200.0,
      "end_time": 789749.0,
      "text": "It hardly happens."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 789773.0,
      "end_time": 793125.0,
      "text": "Because this is evolution, this is the natural ratio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 793149.0,
      "end_time": 797300.0,
      "text": "unlike resistance, which happens in the case of chemicals."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 797270.0,
      "end_time": 800300.0,
      "text": "And thirdly, public demand."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 800496.0,
      "end_time": 805300.0,
      "text": "The more the public demands the reduction of chemicals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 805324.0,
      "end_time": 809169.0,
      "text": "the more growers become aware of the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 809193.0,
      "end_time": 811935.0,
      "text": "that they should, wherever they can and wherever possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 811959.0,
      "end_time": 815890.0,
      "text": "replace the chemical control with biological control."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 815994.0,
      "end_time": 818560.0,
      "text": "Even here, there is another grower,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 818800.0,
      "end_time": 821807.0,
      "text": "you see, very interested in the bugs, the bad ones and the good ones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 821831.0,
      "end_time": 824260.0,
      "text": "wearing this magnifier already on her head,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 824500.0,
      "end_time": 826459.0,
      "text": "just walking safely in her crop."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 827127.0,
      "end_time": 830387.0,
      "text": "Finally, I want to get to my vision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 830411.0,
      "end_time": 832363.0,
      "text": "or, in fact, to my dream."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 832871.0,
      "end_time": 834894.0,
      "text": "Because, you see, this is the reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 834918.0,
      "end_time": 836394.0,
      "text": "Have a look at the gap."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 836418.0,
      "end_time": 838536.0,
      "text": "If we take the overall turnover"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 838560.0,
      "end_time": 841500.0,
      "text": "of the biocontrol industry worldwide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 841290.0,
      "end_time": 842903.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s 250 million dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 844220.0,
      "end_time": 847116.0,
      "text": "And look at the overall pesticide industry"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 847140.0,
      "end_time": 848994.0,
      "text": "in all the crops throughout the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 849337.0,
      "end_time": 852208.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s times 100 or something like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 852232.0,
      "end_time": 853938.0,
      "text": "Twenty-five billion."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 853962.0,
      "end_time": 856577.0,
      "text": "So there is a huge gap to bridge."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 857560.0,
      "end_time": 859223.0,
      "text": "So actually, how can we do it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 859248.0,
      "end_time": 864128.0,
      "text": "How can we bridge, or let&#39;s say, narrow, this gap over the years?"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 864152.0,
      "end_time": 867900.0,
      "text": "First of all, we need to find more robust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 867924.0,
      "end_time": 870536.0,
      "text": "good and reliable biological solutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 870560.0,
      "end_time": 875183.0,
      "text": "more good bugs that we can either mass-produce"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 875207.0,
      "end_time": 877711.0,
      "text": "or actually conserve in the field."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 878273.0,
      "end_time": 882859.0,
      "text": "Secondly, to create even more intensive and strict public demand"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 882883.0,
      "end_time": 886135.0,
      "text": "for the reduction of chemicals in agricultural fresh produce."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 886976.0,
      "end_time": 890734.0,
      "text": "And thirdly, also to increase awareness by the growers"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 890758.0,
      "end_time": 892909.0,
      "text": "to the potential of this industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 893560.0,
      "end_time": 896590.0,
      "text": "And this gap really narrows."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 896830.0,
      "end_time": 898698.0,
      "text": "Step by step, it does narrow."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 899817.0,
      "end_time": 902220.0,
      "text": "So I think my last slide is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 902460.0,
      "end_time": 904311.0,
      "text": "All we are saying -- we can actually sing it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 904335.0,
      "end_time": 906129.0,
      "text": "Give nature a chance."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 906153.0,
      "end_time": 909319.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m saying it on behalf of all the biocontrol practitioners"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 909343.0,
      "end_time": 910656.0,
      "text": "and implementers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 910681.0,
      "end_time": 912902.0,
      "text": "in Israel and abroad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 912926.0,
      "end_time": 914958.0,
      "text": "really give nature a chance."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 914982.0,
      "end_time": 916141.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 916165.0,
      "end_time": 918236.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}